headline: UDR, Inc. Named 2025 Top Workplaces Industry Winner
summary: DENVER, July 17, 2025--UDR, Inc. (the "Company") (NYSE: UDR), a leading multifamily real estate investment trust, announced today that it has earned the distinction of being a 2025 Top Workplaces winner in the Real Estate Industry. Additional details about how UDR builds a great workplace culture are available on the Company’s page of the Top Workplaces website at https://topworkplaces.com/company/udr/.
